description: This guy had a very lucky day. Meeting anyone else except me, he would had gone home empty handed. Getting two words out of him was an impossible task even for me. How did he expect to pass a job interview?! Anyways... he was bored of his supermarket job and wanted to do what he actually trained for at school. He was a car body repairman, which is a pretty solid trade in high demand. Only problem was that he never worked the trade besides practical training at school. I was willing to help him out. Obviously, I had some hidden agenda but the boy had no idea. Not until I made him to undress and show me his body. Then things escalated very quickly. The boy needed money and I wanted to fuck, not very difficult to guess what followed. I gave the boy a nice ride and I hope to see him again.
title: Dirty Scout 192
